{"id":"47f1ca439bcf75ad2b7f66531002df1ef8c65f34e5ebad75a00b57f33e5173f1","text":"计算两个向量之间的叉积。叉积会生成一个结果向量，该向量垂直于两个输入向量。如果在多边形平面中使用两个输入向量，这在尝试查找多边形的法线向量时会很有用。"}
{"id":"38584b10da8233a54a288d585135b46bf72933147d492442bbbea125750112b0","text":"Vector 1"}
{"id":"cb9476332c7fcb5ad8763068ecf2a016a05b29f7977cb4d286610997fd39fe67","text":"叉积计算中的第一个向量。"}
{"id":"eace214ef9a6ada7f46d506e1df6221ea33bebac3749fc443319088cb847642b","text":"Vector 2"}
{"id":"740aac13f098a21de204728c9e628d4cf0396cccb0380db11c4ce05d6d2a0e76","text":"叉积计算中的第二个向量。"}
{"id":"8a7fac9c892cf9041268ec1a6b37392025cf7e7c435a872bbeca59294b6eaca4","text":"Normalize Result"}
{"id":"7743dd6559bbacd2a261f4f61e26cd8bdc60747aa360ac4eee17368e48d92455","text":"启用时（设为 1），叉积结果将是归一化向量。"}
{"id":"35f6e1ebb9b040db4e992f8d8fb554d4bc9ad8ea924c6744adc8ae3f58bc3498","text":"resultXYZ"}
{"id":"5963b1cf571fb4aa47cd695b5f674b28f031f1c0c8ab5d65f15f05b794fc5ed6","text":"叉积结果向量。"}
{"id":"db7dd1ce0d7ea86988255ca35194b0f1bd3ac901a577cbf001917e21a93cd36c","text":"resultX"}
{"id":"29ae71f9ed673ba0ac9f0665be3a580e22f3730cc133352d450ae293b0912204","text":"来自 resultXYZ 输出的 X 分量。"}
{"id":"1559ea0c7d8aa4ad51badbe1b30a3a5d7b82932753dbc63044d02897c487480c","text":"resultY"}
{"id":"d123f179f225b75f5c31d8eb27e55d3e111c3dcb113e1b574dcb3c6f0d2e9162","text":"来自 resultXYZ 输出的 Y 分量。"}
{"id":"153df47561d2ede586a69b0186936cf344555bcbef47ecadd8fbf8b7ce5b2672","text":"resultZ"}
{"id":"862a07bec45906d80eb88bd5c5e3e88c294baf8437e127dce1ee92ec7d457d62","text":"来自 resultXYZ 输出的 Z 分量。"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:1", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:8", "text": "Output Parameters"}
